'''THX servant droids''' were butler/servant [[Droid/Legends|droids]] that resembled [[3PO-series protocol droid/Legends|3PO-series protocol droids]]. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Simon Greyshade/Legends|Simon Greyshade]] owned such a droid. It was modified by [[Venco Autem]] to assassinate Greyshade, but disabled by [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].

